<plot>'The first week of a break-up is like the first time a guy has sex... its awkward...boring....and...we keep telling each other we're doing it right but its a lie.' These are the words of Rafael Casal, a Bay Area spoken word/hip hop artist and the writer and creator of this poem. This piece shows how not only girls have a rough time getting through a break up, but guys do as well.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?545890</url></doc>
